appstream-glib (0.7.0~git20170615-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * [62bc645] New upstream version 0.7.0~git20170615
    + This is an upstream snapshot created with `git archive' from commit
      c74fa38af1cac2d259c62df4d4a0b852375bcbd3.
  * [82c3da3] debian/{control,rules}: Switch to meson. There's a 'configure'
    script, which debhelper uses by default. Pass '-Smeson' to force the meson
    build system.
  * [b54361c] debian/libappstream-glib8.symbols: Update for this release.
    as_get_resource() is dropped, but that is a leaked symbol that shouldn't
    have been exposed anyway. I'm letting it slide.
  * [6b73653] debian/control: Drop intltool. No longer used.
  * [fa5a9d7] Conditionally skip test which requires 'gcab' if it isn't
    installed
  * [55419a6] Run the tests

